# No proprietary project references

This repository (`page-component-object` / `@page-component-object/*`, **PCO** pattern alias) is **public and standalone**. It must not reference proprietary codebases, employers, or client products.

## Do not include in this repo

- Names of internal/proprietary apps (e.g. specific product codenames)
- Paths to private monorepos or internal packages
- Copy-pasted domain models, routes, API paths, or test objects from proprietary apps
- Migration notes that name proprietary projects as consumers or sources of truth

## Do instead

- Use **fictitious** consumer apps under `apps/*` (e.g. `demo-shared`, `vitest-demo`, `storybook-demo`)
- Use generic domain examples: `Items`, `Catalog`, `Workspace`, `ItemDetail`
- Describe patterns abstractly: "prior art from production apps" without naming them
- When porting ideas from private code, **reimplement** with generic names; never paste proprietary identifiers

## Documentation & commits

- `PLAN.md`, `README.md`, package docs, and commit messages must stay generic
- Examples in code comments should use the demo app (`HomeViewTestObject`, `ItemsApiTestObject`) only

## Allowed

- Public libraries (Testing Library, MSW, Storybook, Cypress)
- Public articles and OSS (Kent Dodds, page-o, semantic-matchers)
- Author's own public packages (e.g. `semantic-matchers` on GitHub)
